from\": 277, \"to\": 287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete, who was 19 at the time and knew how old his victim was, admitted to three counts of rape against the child in Milton Keynes in 2014.\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 413, \"end\": 419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Milton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5714171294512495e-23, \"text\": \"Milton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Milton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Milton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athlete\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 301}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"his victim\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 353}, {\"ngram\": \"three counts\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"rape\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 391}, {\"ngram\": \"the child\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Judge Francis Sheridan told Van de Velde at the time: 'Your hopes of representing your country now lie as a shattered dream.'\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 443, \"end\": 450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"score\": 0.9999992210903961, \"rank\": 7.079427171142847e-07, \"text\": \"Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19546\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\"}, {\"begin\": 451, \"end\": 459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheridan_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9850392854084071, \"rank\": 0.015176559247080694, \"text\": \"Sheridan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheridan_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheridan_Crane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 477}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 489}, {\"ngram\": \"Your hopes\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"your country\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"a shattered dream\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, he was released in 2017 even though he had only served one year of his sentence and continued his volleyball career.\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one year\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"his sentence\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 652}, {\"ngram\": \"his volleyball career\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And despite his conviction, the 29-year-old was still picked for the upcoming Olympic games this summer alongside teammate Matthew Immers.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his conviction\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"the upcoming Olympic games\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"teammate Matthew Immers\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Van de Velde will not be staying with other athletes in the Olympic Village, as is the tradition with every other competitor, according toNL Times.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 895, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9396695411121429e-16, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"the tradition\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 931}, {\"ngram\": \"every other competitor\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"toNL Times\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He requested to seek his own alternative accommodation and will also avoid any media duties after matches, leaving those solely to Immers, 23.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his own alternative accommodation\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"any media duties\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"matches\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"Immers\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde will reportedly speak to journalists before the games begin, though, to explain his decision to stay away from the village, reportsBILD.\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"journalists\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"his decision\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"reportsBILD\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After he was released, Van de Velde said in 2018: 'I cannot reverse it, so I will have to bear the consequences.\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"the consequences\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been the biggest mistake of my life.'\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest mistake\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1423}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last month, the Dutch Olympic committee, known as NOC*NSF, and the volleyball association Nevobo gave Van de Velde their backing and said there was 'no reason' to exclude him from taking part.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5485560042643866e-21, \"text\": \"Dutch Olympic committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}, {\"begin\": 1488, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NOC*NSF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the volleyball association Nevobo\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1534}, {\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"their backing\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"no reason\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But following backlash over his inclusion, including from the British Olympic Association which has 'grave concerns' over it, the Dutch association were forced to take extra measures.\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1694, \"end\": 1721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9563623904116715, \"rank\": 0.045597920310488545, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"backlash\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"his inclusion\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1673}, {\"ngram\": \"grave concerns\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"extra measures\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokesman for the Dutch committee said: 'NOC*NSF have come to these measures after discussions with the beach volleyballer and his teammates.\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1